<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣١٥٤ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادُ بْنُ زَيْدٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا نُصِيبُ فِي مَغَازِينَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٩٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْعَسَلَ وَالْعِنَبَ، فَنَأْكُلُهُ وَلَا نَرْفَعُهُ.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>